      "text": [
        "346 - وَقَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «أَعْقَلُ مَا يَكُونُ اَلْمُؤْمِنُ عِنْدَ مَوْتِهِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.346 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said: \"The believer is most rational (aware) at the time of their death.\""
        ]
      }
    }
